1. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - The paper deals with the computation of topological invariants of 3D objects, which is a common topic in computational geometry.
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper uses 3D digital images as input and computes topological invariants, which is a common topic in computer vision.
3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper deals with the computation of cohomology and cohomology ring, which are topics in discrete mathematics.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with the representation and computation of 3D objects, which is a common topic in computer graphics.
5. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper presents algorithms for the computation of topological invariants, which is a topic in numerical analysis.
